author: Reuters Editorial
title: Vectrus Q4 Earnings Per Share $3.70
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - Vectrus Inc:
* VECTRUS ANNOUNCES STRONG FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL-YEAR 2017 RESULTS; ISSUES 2018 GUIDANCE AND FIVE-YEAR GROWTH PLAN
* SEES ‍2018 DILUTED EPS $2.70 TO $3.22​ * SEES ‍2018 CASH PROVIDED BY OPERATING ACTIVITIES $35.0 MILLION TO $39.0 MILLION​
* ‍EXPECT 2018 FULL-YEAR OPERATING MARGIN TO BE IN RANGE OF 3.6 PERCENT TO 4.0 PERCENT​ Source text for Eikon:
